ok\">George Bull (15 July 1998). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=AZWfE3YOMkQC&amp;pg=PA3\"><i>Michelangelo: A Biography</i></a>. St. Martin's Press. pp.&#160;3\u2013. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-312-18746-0\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-312-18746-0\">978-0-312-18746-0</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Michelangelo%3A+A+Biography&amp;rft.pages=3-&amp;rft.pub=St.+Martin%27s+Press&amp;rft.date=1998-07-15&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-312-18746-0&amp;rft.au=George+Bull&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DAZWfE3YOMkQC%26pg%3DPA3&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACatafalque\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Schraven, Minou (2014). <i>Festive Funerals in Early Modern Italy: The Art and Culture of Conspicuous Commemoration</i>. Ashgate Publishing. p.&#160;203. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780754665243\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780754665243\">9780754665243</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Festive+Funerals+in+Early+Modern+Italy%3A+The+Art+and+Culture+of+Conspicuous+Commemoration&amp;rft.pages=203&amp;rft.pub=Ashgate+Publishing&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.isbn=9780754665243&amp;rft.aulast=Schraven&amp;rft.aufirst=Minou&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACatafalque\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li